data.description: HOME FOR THE HOLIDAYS! You can move right in and start enjoying all the things that make downtown Winter Garden special, especially during the holiday season! Secure your homestead exemption for 2024 now. Located in the downtown Winter Garden Golf Cart district, this beautiful home has been loved and well maintained, but it's time for the owner to downsize. Covington Chase/Covington Park community is only a short golf cart ride to Plant Street. There you'll find boutique shopping, fabulous dining, coffee shops, bars, the Saturday Farmer's Market, Winter Garden theatre,  Scoops, Kelly's and Rita's frozen treats, City Hall, Splash Pad, Crooked Can Brewery, Plant St. Market, and lots of family friendly seasonal and holiday events.  This 2014 home features a great room floor plan with split bedrooms and a fully fenced backyard that backs up to the West Orange Trail. Seller will provide a one year home warranty at closing and the buyer has the option to transfer the Massey preventative maintenance termite bond for even more peace of mind. You'll love sitting on your screened lanai or barbecuing on the new open paver patio while bird watching or just enjoying the fresh air.  The well equipped kitchen is outfitted with 42 inch maple cabinets, black appliances, tiled backsplash, granite countertops, breakfast bar seating and a closet pantry. The open layout of the great room is perfect for entertaining with plenty of space to gather in the kitchen and dining area. Casually dine at the breakfast bar, or in the adjacent dining area. One of the best features is the huge master suite which includes a large sitting area and direct slider access to the screened lanai. Dual walk-in closets flank the en-suite master bathroom which has a raised height granite topped double vanity, tiled walk-in shower and private commode room. Low maintenance diagonal ceramic tile flooring covers most of the home and newer vinyl plank flooring was installed in the master bedroom and one guest bedroom. Only the spacious front facing bedroom has carpet. Ceiling fans and 5-6" baseboards throughout the home. The St. Augustine lawn is nicely landscaped and irrigated with a metered sprinkler system on timer. Even better, the home has gutters and downspouts to help direct the rainwater away from the home. An indoor laundry room includes full sized Whirlpool Cabrio Platinum washer and dryer. In the two car garage there is an automatic door opener, laundry sink, and energy efficient hybrid hot water heater that allows you to easily adjust settings for your comfort.  Very reasonable HOA fees and the neighborhood community pool is just a short golf cart ride away. Come be a part of downtown Winter Garden!
